# Neurex Project Directory Structure

Registry-first React UI monorepo (pnpm + Turborepo). Install flow:

`packages/registry` в†’ `packages/cli` в†’ consumer project (user-owned code).

Do not blur package responsibilities. Public APIs live in `package.json` `exports` only; `dist/` is publish output; never deep-import `src/` or `dist/` from outside a package.

---

## Repository Root

```
neurex/
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ .agent/                 # Agent continuity/state (see AGENTS.md в†’ CONTINUITY.md)
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ .cursor/rules/          # Cursor rules (*.mdc)
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ apps/                   # Workspace apps
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ docs/                   # Architecture and workflow documentation
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ packages/               # Publishable workspace packages
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ AGENTS.md               # Repo-specific agent contract (always applied)
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ README.md
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ package.json            # Root scripts (turbo orchestration)
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ pnpm-workspace.yaml     # apps/*, packages/*
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ turbo.json
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ tsconfig.json / tsconfig.base.json
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ eslint.config.mjs
в””в”Ђв”Ђ prettier.config.mjs
```

**Ignore for source work:** `node_modules/`, `dist/`, `.turbo/`, `.pnpm-store/`, `.tmp/`

