## `packages/tokens`

Token dependency chain: **primitives в†’ brand в†’ semantics в†’ component tokens**; **themes** override semantics per mode; **presets** are config only.

**Active semantic groups (11):** `color`, `action`, `border`, `elevation`, `radius`, `spacing`, `size`, `motion`, `typography`, `outline`, `layout`. Authoring for `color` lives under `semantics/color/` (merged into one `color` namespace). Canonical rules: `docs/TOKENS.md`.

```
packages/tokens/
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ src/
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ primitives/       # Raw values only (color, spacing, radius, motion, z-index, shadow, вЂ¦)
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ brand/            # Brand palette (references primitives)
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ semantics/        # Usage intent (references brand/primitives)
в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ color/        # Optional subfolder; merges into top-level color.* paths
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ components/       # Per-component tokens (semantic references only)
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ themes/           # Mode overrides вЂ” same paths as semantics (border.*, action.*, color.*)
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ presets/          # Preset config (not a token layer)
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ engine/           # Token engine: read/transform, validate, report
в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ resolver/     # reference + graph traversal
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ reference/
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ graph/
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ shared/
в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ validator/    # build-failing layer contracts
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ layers/
в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ governance/   # non-blocking reports
в”‚   в”‚       в”њв”Ђв”Ђ report/
в”‚   в”‚       в””в”Ђв”Ђ audit/
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ generators/
в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ inputs/       # Source inputs for generation
в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ outputs/css/  # CSS generator
в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ outputs/dtcg/ # DTCG JSON generator
в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ shared/       # Shared generator utilities
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ types/            # Token/type definitions + authoring factories
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ index.ts          # Package entry
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ scripts/              # CLI entrypoints (parallel to src/, not inside src/)
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ write-style-outputs.ts
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ governance-report.ts
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ clean-imports.ts
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ vitest.config.ts      # Vitest project config (node)
в””в”Ђв”Ђ test/                 # resolver, validator, generator, governance, semantic-audit
```

**Exports:** `.`, `./tokens.css`, `./theme.css` (generated; do not hand-write CSS).

**Elevation chain:** primitive `z-index.*` / `shadow.*` в†’ semantic `elevation.*` в†’ component slot tokens в†’ UI `z-(--nx-*)` / `shadow-(--nx-*)` in `*.variants.ts`.

