## `packages/ui`

Reference implementations organized in three composition layers. Each item is a
**PascalCase folder** with:

- `ComponentName.tsx`
- `ComponentName.types.ts`
- `ComponentName.variants.ts`

```
packages/ui/
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ src/
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ index.ts              # Public API вЂ” 41 primitives exported today
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ utils/                # Shared UI utilities
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ components/
в”‚       в”њв”Ђв”Ђ primitives/       # 41 bundled primitives
в”‚       в”њв”Ђв”Ђ blocks/           # Pilot: FormField, Sidebar
в”‚       в””в”Ђв”Ђ templates/        # Pilot: DashboardShell
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ vitest.config.ts          # Vitest project config (jsdom)
в””в”Ђв”Ђ test/
    в”њв”Ђв”Ђ public-api.test.ts
    в””в”Ђв”Ђ components/<Name>/    # Variant + render tests (primitives only)
```

**Primitives:** Accordion, Alert, AlertDialog, Autocomplete, Avatar, Badge, Button, Card, Checkbox, CheckboxGroup, Collapsible, Combobox, ContextMenu, Dialog, Drawer, Field, Fieldset, Form, Input, Menu, Menubar, Meter, NavigationMenu, NumberField, OtpField, Popover, PreviewCard, Progress, RadioGroup, ScrollArea, Select, Separator, Slider, Switch, Tabs, Textarea, Toast, Toggle, ToggleGroup, Toolbar, Tooltip.

**Pilot blocks/templates:** FormField, Sidebar, DashboardShell вЂ” registry + CLI installable; sandbox QA in progress. See [UI_COMPOSITION.md](../../docs/UI_COMPOSITION.md).

Base UI (`@base-ui/react`) is internal; preserve accessibility when editing.

