## `packages/registry`

Source of truth for what the CLI installs. **No install logic outside registry metadata.**

```
packages/registry/
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ src/
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ index.ts
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ registry.types.ts
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ validate-registry.ts
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ validate-registry-item.ts
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ items/            # One file per installable item (metadata)
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ styles/           # Registry style entries (e.g. theme.ts)
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ utilities/        # Shared utility metadata (e.g. cn.ts)
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ templates/
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ primitives/<Name>/   # Primitive install templates
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ blocks/<Name>/       # Block install templates
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ templates/<Name>/    # Template install templates
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ shared/utils/        # e.g. cn.ts
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ styles/              # tokens.css, theme.css templates
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ scripts/
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ sync-component-templates.mjs   # Sync ui primitives в†’ templates
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ sync-block-templates.mjs       # Sync ui blocks/templates в†’ templates
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ sync-all-templates.mjs         # Run both sync scripts
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ check-registry-styles-sync.mjs # Verify style templates vs token output
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ lib/registry-styles-sync.mjs   # Shared compare helpers for style sync
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ registry-item-generator.mjs
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ vitest.config.ts
в””в”Ђв”Ђ test/
    в”њв”Ђв”Ђ validate-registry.test.ts
    в””в”Ђв”Ђ registry-styles-sync.test.ts
```

**Exports:** `.`, `./templates/*` (templates ship with the package).

Every registry item must declare: files, dependencies, utilities, styles, target paths.

