## Where to Change What

| Task | Primary location |
|------|------------------|
| Token values / layers | `packages/tokens/src/` |
| Semantic organization / audit | `packages/tokens/src/engine/governance/`, `docs/TOKENS.md` |
| Generated CSS | Build pipeline only (`packages/tokens` build) |
| Component behavior (reference) | `packages/ui/src/components/{primitives,blocks,templates}/` |
| What gets installed / paths | `packages/registry/src/items/` + `templates/`; consumer flat `paths.components` |
| Install/init/update behavior | `packages/cli/src/` |
| Visual verification (monorepo smoke) | `apps/playground/` вЂ” maintenance-only; consumer truth in external sandbox ([TESTING.md](../../docs/TESTING.md#verification-surfaces)) |
| Maintainer workflow | `AGENTS.md` В§ Change workflow; branch off `dev`, PR to `dev` last |
| Architecture contracts | `docs/` + `AGENTS.md` |

After editing `packages/ui` components, run `pnpm registry:sync` to refresh registry templates when templates should match UI (primitives + blocks/templates).

After editing overlay `*.variants.ts` stacking/shadow classes or component elevation tokens, sync registry templates and run `pnpm tokens:check`.

